>> #
>> #       Load water and ions for TIP3P + Li/Merz monovalent ions 
>> #       + Joung-Chetham monovalent ions
>> #       + Li/Merz highly charged ions (+2 to +4, 12-6 normal usage set)
>> #
>> #       Note: the Li/Merz monovalent set is loaded only to get Tl+,
